    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know i should see a doctor but i just dont want to deal with the wait times for something that might be nothing. honestly it feels more like just being out of shape than a medical emergency. what if i just try taking two puffs instead of one next time i feel it? would that be okay as a temporary fix until i can get around to a checkup?",
