      "content": "It's understandable that you're frustrated with the wait times, but it's not advisable to increase your inhaler dosage without medical supervision. Doubling up on puffs of salbutamol could lead to serious side effects, including worsening your asthma or causing other health issues. It's essential to have your symptoms evaluated by a healthcare professional to ensure your asthma is properly managed. In the meantime, try to avoid overexertion and focus on maintaining a healthy lifestyle. Your safety is the top priority, and a checkup is a necessary step to ensure your well-being.",
